{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I was glad when they said to me,\n"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Let’s go to Yahweh’s house!",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Our feet are standing within your gates, Jerusalem!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Jerusalem is built as a city that is compact together,"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "where the tribes go up, even Yah’s tribes, according to an ordinance for Israel,"
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "to give thanks to Yahweh’s name."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "For there are set thrones for judgment, the thrones of David’s house."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Pray for the peace of Jerusalem. Those who love you will prosper."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Peace be within your walls, and prosperity within your palaces."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "For my brothers’ and companions’ sakes, I will now say, "
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Peace be within you.",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "9",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "For the sake of the house of Yahweh our God, I will seek your good."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}